Usage instructions:

You also need to get the python-bugzilla library:
git clone git://gitorious.org/opensuse/python-bugzilla.git -b suse

Then link the bugzilla folder inside the suse_bug_reporter folder:
% ln -s python-bugzilla/bugzilla suse_bug_reporter/

Then, use the tool from the parent folder of where you have the repo cloned:

$ PYTHONPATH=. python suse_bug_reporter/bin/susebugreporter.py [-h] {argument}
